<H3> <TI>   Yunnan Secretary Addresses Graduates of Deng Study Class </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yunnan Secretary Addresses Graduates of Deng Study Class </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK2704151394 Kunming Yunnan People's Radio Network in 
