<F P=100> Near East &amp; South Asia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Luo Gan Receives Bangladesh Law Minister </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Luo Gan Receives Bangladesh Law Minister </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2904055094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0530 GMT 29 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2904055094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

