<H3> <TI>   Hu Jintao Meets Argentine President Menem </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hu Jintao Meets Argentine President Menem </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Views Argentine Farm 23 Apr </H4>

<F P=102> OW2604002994 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0354 
GMT 24 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW2604002994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By reporter Lin Minzhong (2651 3046 1813)] </F>
  [Text] Buenos Aires, 23 Apr (XINHUA) -- A CPC delegation 
led by Hu Jintao, member of the Standing Committee of the 
Political Bureau and member of the Secretariat of the CPC 
Central Committee, visited (Jinhehuan) Farm in Argentina on 23 
April. 
  Hu Jintao and his party arrived at the farm, located some 80 
km west of Buenos Aires, by automobile at 1200. Cowboys on 
horseback, in Gaucho herdsman's costumes, lined up to welcome 
the distinguished Chinese guests. The hospitable host briefed 
Hu Jintao and his party on the situation of the farm. The main 
crops of the 1,400-hectare farm are wheat, oats, and forage 
grass. 
  On the farm, Hu Jintao and members of the delegation watched 
the Gaucho rodeo and folk dance performances with great 
interest; they also had some delicious roast beef. 
  In the evening, the delegation watched Argentina's unique 
Tango dance performance. 

</TEXT>

