<H3> <TI>   Shandong Publishes Export-Oriented Economic Guide </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shandong Publishes Export-Oriented Economic Guide </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2904060294 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in 
