<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cosponsored by the Shandong branch of the XINHUA 
News Agency and the Shandong Provincial Commission for Foreign 
Economic Relations and Trade, WAIXIANG JINGJI DAOBAO 
[EXPORT-ORIENTED ECONOMIC GUIDE] started publication in Jinan a 
few days ago. This is the first newspaper of the province that 
specially serves the development of the export-oriented economy. 
Leading Comrades Li Lanqing, Jiang Chunyun, Wu Yi, and Zhao 
